title: Ganesh: Lord of the Lakes
subTitle: The film captures, for the first time in natural history television, a male tiger mating with females from three generations of the same bloodline. Set in the lakes area of Ranthambhore, it follows young male Ganesh, known for his bold hunting, charging through open water, and the resident tigress, Riddhi.
